descriptionHTML:
Refresh Your Skin and Mind.
A WatchFace from Isshindo-Honpo is out now.
This design refers to the Japanese traditional performance , Kabuki's Make-up.


-----------------------------------
It's possible to change two design of WatchFace from Watch Face App.
It corresponds to both round and square sizes, and has an optimized ambient mode.
※Some devices or terminals only shows the digital watch when using the ambient mode.
